In May 2020, we asked a representative sample of more than 2,000 Americans to rate their trust of the CDC, the Postal Service, and FEMA. We surveyed most of the group again in October.

We found about a 10% decline in trust of the CDC over that period. https://t.co/EhslnOBsn6 https://t.co/SrdpjWrMF2
